.RB \[lq] A4 \[rq],
.RB \[lq] B5 \[rq],
.RB \[lq] C5 \[rq],
.RB \[lq] com10 \[rq],
.RB \[lq] DL \[rq],
.RB \%\[lq] executive \[rq],
