.RB \%\[lq] letter \[rq],
and
.RB \[lq] monarch \[rq].
.
These are matched case-insensitively.
.
The
.B \-p
option overrides any setting in the device description file
.IR DESC .
.
If neither specifies a paper format,
\[lq]letter\[rq] is assumed.
.
